OL,3,CIncrease in candidates for jobs, study
OL,4,Csuggests
OL,6,FThe number of candidates for
OL,7,Fadvertised jobs has increased
OL,8,Fsubstantially, according to recruiters.
OL,10,FThe recent increase was largely
OL,11,Fbecause of job losses amid company
OL,12,Frestructuring efforts and
OL,13,Fredundancies, as well as a reduction
OL,14,Fin recruitment activity, according to
OL,15,Fresearch among 400 recruitment
OL,16,Fagencies.
OL,18,FDemand for staff weakened in April,
OL,19,Fsaid the Recruitment and Employment
OL,20,FConfederation (REC) and KPMG.
