OL,3,CIncrease in candidates for jobs, study
OL,4,Csuggests
OL,6,FNeil Carberry, REC chief executive,
OL,7,Fsaid: "Given the wave of costs firms
OL,8,Ffaced in April, maintaining the
OL,9,Fgradual improvement in numbers we have
OL,10,Fseen over the past few months is on
OL,11,Fthe good end of our expectations.
OL,13,F"While we are yet to see real momentum
OL,14,Fbuild, hopes of an improving picture
OL,15,Fin the second half of the year should
OL,16,Fbe buoyed by today's data.
